OL,3,CGovernment ups subsidies for GP
OL,4,Cappointments by #10 in Jersey
OL,6,F's government has increased its
OL,7,Ffunding for GP visits by #10.
OL,9,FThis latest reduction brings the
OL,10,Foverall subsidy for face-to-face
OL,11,Fappointments, surgery consultations
OL,12,Fand home visits to #50.28.
OL,14,FThe amount residents currently pay
OL,15,Fafter that subsidy ranges
OL,16,Fconsiderably, between #25 and #51 per
OL,17,Fvisit.
OL,19,FThis is because GP practices on the
OL,20,Fisland are all privately owned so they
OL,21,Fmake the final decision on pricing.
