OL,3,CGovernment ups subsidies for GP
OL,4,Cappointments by #10 in Jersey
OL,6,FThe Government says as patient charges
OL,7,Fcan make it harder for some to access
OL,8,Fhealth services.
OL,10,FDeputy Feltham explains: "We really
OL,11,Fdon't want the cost of visiting a GP
OL,12,Fto be a barrier that prevents people
OL,13,Ffrom seeking early help from their GP
OL,14,Fwhen they need it."
