OL,6,FGordon Callander from the Primary Care
OL,7,FBody which represents GPs in Jersey
OL,8,Fadds: "We welcome any government
OL,9,Finitiative that reduces costs to
OL,10,Fpatients to ease any financial
OL,11,Fbarriers, especially to those most in
OL,12,Fneed."
OL,14,FThe subsidy will come into effect from
OL,15,FMonday 20 May.
